column5: This is a quick hello to everyone. I am an avid fisherman of Lake Simcoe to muskoka and everywhere in between. I love ice fishing and hanging out with good friends on the water, since they are the ones that own the boats, not me.  I cannot wait to share stories and pics as the come.  If I'm not on the water I can be found wandering the woods hunting.
Welcome, good bunch of folks around here!
Welcome to the zoo!  You'll have fun here.  Lottsa info to be shared.
Like the tag name.  Justcuz you can,justcuz you want, and justcuz.  Yup. it,s a wild ride at times. Put on your thick skin suit and jump in.  Welcome.
